videos.headline: SMU responds with 24-yard passing TD
videos.description: Not long after Temple opens the scoring, Tyler Page gets the Mustangs on the board with a 24-yard receiving touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (SMU responds with 24-yard passing TD) 2020/11/07 ESHEET

videos.headline: Jones breaks free for 75-yard Temple TD
videos.description: Temple scores first as Trad Beatty tosses the short pass and Randle Jones takes the 75-yard touchdown to the house.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Jones breaks free for 75-yard Temple TD) 2020/11/07 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ruley runs it in for 3-yard rushing TD
videos.description: Tayvon Ruley powers his way to the goal line to help Temple regain the lead late in the first quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Ruley runs it in for 3-yard rushing TD) 2020/11/07 ESHEET

videos.headline: Page shakes off 3 defenders and scores for SMU
videos.description: Tyler Page avoids being tackled and takes off for the 44-yard touchdown early in the second half.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Page shakes off 3 defenders and scores for SMU) 2020/11/07 ESHEET

videos.headline: Granson easily scores SMU's third TD
videos.description: Shane Buechele throws the perfect ball to Kylen Granson, who walks into the end zone to complete the 24-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Granson easily scores SMU's third TD) 2020/11/07 ESHEET

videos.headline: SMU's Williams leaves everyone in the dust
videos.description: TaMerik Williams takes advantage of the open field and scores a 49-yard rushing touchdown extending the Mustangs' lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (SMU's Williams leaves everyone in the dust) 2020/11/07 ESHEET
